# TodoMVC React — Project Memory

This is what `/init` should produce after Phase 2 (tweak to match reality).

## Stack
- React 17 (Phase 6 upgrades to 18+)
- webpack 5 + webpack-dev-server (Phase 6 migrates to Vite)
- Jest + React Testing Library (scaffolded in Phase 2)
- ESLint — `eslint:recommended` only (Phase 6 tightens this)

## Commands
- `npm ci`, `npm run dev` (:8080), `npm test`, `npm run lint`, `npm run build`

## Conventions
- Components in `src/`
- Co-located `*.test.jsx`

## Known pitfalls
- TodoMVC spec tests are strict — don't change URL fragment routing (`#/`, `#/active`, `#/completed`)
- Canonical example has no persistence — adding it is a valid Phase 6 Track B feature

## Don't touch
- `node_modules/`, `dist/`
- webpack configs (Phase 6 replaces them)
